title: The Dream Sourcebook - A. Lemley & P. Koch-Sheras Mobi/Epub/
description: Koch-Sheras and Lemley provide broad coverage of dreams, ranging from ancient theories about their meanings down to contemporary approaches to their interpretation. They offer basic information on how to remember and record dreams and on what to do once you have ensnared a few for analysis. They include a solid, useful chapter on forming a dream group as well as a levelheaded one on psychic phenomena in dreams. A good introduction for general collections
